==Proposed redirect==
This page had been redirected to [[Ashkenazi Jews]], but it has now been changed to [[Ashkenaz (disambiguation)]]. However, the page view statistics indicate that [[Ashkenazi Jews]] is what people are looking for when they type in "Ashkenazi", and hence it is the [[WP:PRIMARYTOPIC|primary topic]]. "Askenazi" gets about 400 hits a day, while [[Ashkenazi_(surname)]] (which is the only link in the hatnote) gets only 20 visits per day. [[Ashkenazi Jews]] gets about 1800. [[User:StAnselm|<b>St</b>]][[Special:Contributions/StAnselm|Anselm]] ([[User talk:StAnselm|talk]]) 22:40, 28 August 2011 (UTC)
